text: Salvador Suárez (born 14 January 1948) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
